{"word":"ἄγνοια","slug":"ἄγνοια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἄγνοια, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀγνοέω\">ἀγνοέω</a></el>] ‘state of being uninformed’, <b><i>ignorance</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> lack of awareness and therefore excusable (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀγνόημα\">ἀγνόημα</a></el> <a href='B:650 9:7'>Hb 9:7</a>)<b> <a href='B:510 3:17'>Ac 3:17</a>; <a href='B:510 17:30'>17:30</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> disregard of what is morally appropriate <b><a href='B:560 4:18'>Eph 4:18</a>; <a href='B:670 1:14'>1 Pt 1:14</a>; <a href='B:680 2:13'>2 Pt 2:13</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀγνόημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἁγνός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}